        "\n",
        "# Love-OS Verification Notebook (English)\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook visualizes and validates the V/R/I equations defined in **TECHNICAL_SPECS.md**.\n",
        "We simulate **Throughput (I)**, **Efficiency (η)**, and **Latency (L)**, and perform sensitivity analysis,\n",
        "A/B experiment simulation, and a simple parameter fitting demo.\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Note:** This is a demo with synthetic parameters. For serious use, calibrate parameters with your real logs.\n"
      ]
